text: Lena () is a rural locality (a village) in Taymasovsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 40 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Yermolayevo, 10 km from Novotaymasovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Lena, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
